We’ve combined the power of Google with the experience of AdSense to create Auto ads. It’s our latest automation feature aimed to give you more time to create content and less time worrying about monetization. 

And we’re not stopping there. 

(But that’s another story.)

You focus on your content, we’ll be right behind you.
  
We know that great content takes time. That’s why we make it simple and quick to set up. So you can sit back, relax and concentrate on what you do best.

It's easy to get started with Auto Ads. Just add one piece of code to your pages and let Google do the rest. Plus, you even can tailor the experience to make sure you’re completely happy with it. 

Piece of cake.

Is Auto ads right for my site?

Auto ads is a customizable experience. Whether you’re a travel blogger, a pastry chef or a news reporter, it provides a tailored solution for every individual site.
